properties.title: Wiwannihütte
properties.description: The Wiwannihütte is situated on a terrace below the Öugstchummhorn and Wiwannihorn, directly opposite the high Valais peaks. Not only the incomparable panorama, but also the many easy climbing possibilities make it a popular destination. Varied hikes and a via ferrata from the Blatschiedertal valley lead to the hut.
